1. Configure your credentials in your settings.xml 
     <server>
       <id>google-seaside-webdav-repo</id>
       <username>john.doe</username>
       <password>yourGoogleCodePassword</password>
     </server>
     <server>
       <id>google-seaside-webdav-site</id>
       <username>john.doe</username>
       <password>yourGoogleCodePassword</password>
     </server>

2. Invoke Maven
mvn release:prepare -Dusername=john.doe -Dpassword=yourGoogleCodePassword
mvn release:perform -Dusername=john.doe -Dpassword=yourGoogleCodePassword -DrepositoryId=google-seaside-webdav-repo